类 Client

  • java.lang.Object
    • Client

  • public class Client
extends java.lang.Object
    This cass is a basic client with no GUI helper.

    The class is used for Client with basic functions (in Operation enum) with simple Scanner to interact with users. To tranfer the command and file data, users can type the file path for this class to read, or type the md5 code or the content diretly. (Notice :if you wanna type the content directly, you may have to add the word "type " before the content.)

    版本:
    1.0
    作者:
    Mou Ynagchen
    另请参阅:
    Client.Operation

    • 方法详细资料

      • calculateMD5

        public static java.lang.String calculateMD5(byte[] bytes)
        If the file was provided by directly typed or offering the file path , the method will transfer the context to MD5 code.
        参数:
        bytes - the content in the form of byte
        返回:
        the MD5 code of content

      • handelDlete

        private static void handelDlete(java.lang.String[] args)
                         throws java.io.IOException
        This method used the Javalin to organise the command, it will send the command end with "/key/delete", the server will return a string with the information about whether the operation is correctly executed.

        The key refers to the md5 code of the file. If the user type the path or the content directly it will invoke the Read in method to get the md5 code.

        参数:
        args - the whole command sent by main method
        抛出:
        java.io.IOException - throws when the client can' connect to the server correctly.
        另请参阅:
        Readin(String[])

      • handleCompare

        private static void handleCompare(java.lang.String[] args)
                           throws java.io.IOException
        This method used the Javalin to organise the command, it will send the command end with "/k1/compare/k2", the server will return a string with the information about the simple difference and the Levenshtein-distance.

        The k1 and k2 refers to the md5 codes of the files. If the user type the path or the content directly it will invoke the Read in method to get the md5 code.It will print error massage if the files doesn't exist in the database.

        参数:
        args - the whole command sent by main method
        抛出:
        java.io.IOException - throws when the client can' connect to the server correctly.
        另请参阅:
        Readin(String[])

      • handleDownload

        private static void handleDownload(java.lang.String[] args)
                            throws java.io.IOException
        This method used the Javalin to organise the command, it will send the command end with "/key", the server will return a string with the information about whether the file is successfully download to the path.(the command will attach the output path in the header "path")

        The key refers to the md5 code of the file. If the user type the path or the content directly it will invoke the Read in method to get the md5 code.It will print error massage if the files doesn't exist in the database.

        参数:
        args - the whole command sent by main method
        抛出:
        java.io.IOException - throws when the client can' connect to the server correctly.
        另请参阅:
        Readin(String[])

      • handleExists

        private static void handleExists(java.lang.String[] args)
                          throws java.io.IOException
        This method used the Javalin to organise the command, it will send the command end with "/key/exist", the server will return a string with the information about whether the file exists

        The key refers to the md5 code of the file. If the user type the path or the content directly it will invoke the Read in method to get the md5 code.

        参数:
        args - the whole command sent by main method
        抛出:
        java.io.IOException - throws when the client can' connect to the server correctly.
        另请参阅:
        Readin(String[])

      • handleList

        private static void handleList()
                        throws java.io.IOException
        This method used the Javalin to organise the command, it will send the command end with "/list", the server will return a string with the information about all the files in json(including md5, file length, and a overview within 100 words)

        we will ues ObjectMapper and JsonNode to make the information readable and print it.It will print error massage if the file doesn't exist.

        抛出:
        java.io.IOException - throws when the client can' connect to the server correctly.

      • handleUpload

        private static void handleUpload(java.lang.String[] args)
                          throws java.io.IOException
        This method used the Javalin to organise the command, it will send the command end with "/key", the server will return a string with the information about whether the file is successfully uploaded to the database.(the command will attach the content of the file as bytes in the body of request)

        The key refers to the md5 code of the file. If the user type the path or the content directly it will invoke the Read in method to get the md5 code.It will print error massage if the files already exist in the database or the md5 doesn't match with the file content.

        参数:
        args - the whole command sent by main method
        抛出:
        java.io.IOException - throws when the client can' connect to the server correctly.
        另请参阅:
        Readin(String[])

      • main

        public static void main(java.lang.String[] args)
        This method is the main process

        The mission of the method is to read the command for scanner and choose the operation types according the first word of the command.

        It may also pass the whole command (split with blank-space) to the handle-Operation methods. If the command doesn't calls it will invoke printUsage method to print the list of operations
        另请参阅:
        handleList(), handelDlete(String[]), handleCompare(String[]), handleDownload(String[]), handleExists(String[]), handleUpload(String[]), printUsage()

      • parseOperation

        public static Client.Operation parseOperation(java.lang.String op)
        This method is used to transfer the String for the operations to enum type.
        参数:
        op - The word users typed to assign the operation type
        返回:
        The corresponding operation type in the enum class.

      • printUsage

        private static void printUsage()
        If the command of user sent to scanner isn't readable or does't match to any operation, this method will print the list of available operations and the correct command form.

      • Readin

        private static java.lang.String Readin(java.lang.String[] arg)
        If the file was offered by the file path, this method will turn it to context in string. It can also detect the charset of the file, print it, and turn it into UTF-8
        参数:
        arg - the the whole command sent by main method
        返回:
        the context of the file
